{
  "stem": "19218.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I remember the first night when they gave us a piece of bread and I went to sleep and I put the bread in my striped uniform pants, rolled the pants up, put it under my-- under my head.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Of course, when I woke up in the morning, it was gone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "The bread wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "That was my first lesson.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And since then-- since then, every time I got food, they can't take it out of my stomach.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I immediately ate everything which I ever had laid my hands on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, even the-- the-- the-- they called them stubendienst, which means the guy in charge of the barrack, which was an inmate also, but he was above everybody else.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "He had some special privileges.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "He was dishing out the food and he had better food to eat than us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "They were very strict.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "If they ever caught a guy that would steal your piece of bread, he actually was sentenced to death.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They would kill him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Inmates would kill him simply because we all received the same piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "If you take it away from me, that means I'm going to starve to death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And this was-- it's like a code of honor between-- between the-- between the prisoners, between us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "But anyway, of course I didn't know who took it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And from then on, as I indicated, whatever I got, I ate immediately.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "They took me to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bauhof commander.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were usually asking for certain tradespeople.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was really a-- a-- a-- a joke with them because everybody felt, well, if I'm a tradesman, I have a better chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're going to need me so I can become anything-- whatever they wanted me to become.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
